{"tid":2373224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<8000萬票總統> 華盛頓滿街軍警  道路封閉 儼如死城","createTime":"2021-01-20T09:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T01:34:42.000Z","uid":227801,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4216fbb690330372045218e796eaad5e7c45bd24","tid":2373224,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210120/QGRIKHZ2NJD47CQ2AMRACXQ6J4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210120%2FQGRIKHZ2NJD47CQ2AMRACXQ6J4%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=a22143e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210120%2FQGRIKHZ2NJD47CQ2AMRACXQ6J4%2F&h=44296fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210120/QGRIKHZ2NJD47CQ2AMRACXQ6J4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）美國總統當選人拜登宣誓就職前夕，《蘋果》記者在華盛頓特區直擊，由於擔心繼本月初美國國會致命衝突事件重演，當局把華盛頓特區全市及週邊地區的保安措施，提升至前所未見般嚴密，絕大部份道路被封，儼如死城。當地居民表示，對警力佈防之重感到憂慮，坦言「以為活在第三世界」。<br />\n<br />\n在總統就職典禮舉行前夕，連接馬利蘭州及維珍尼亞州到華盛頓的高速公路，全部皆有州警駐守，隨時截查可疑車輛。而大部份連接市中心的大橋，都不容許車輛由其他州分開進華盛頓。<br />\n<br />\n.......................................<br />\n<br />\n來自秘魯的Rodrigo Nadal，在唐人街居住了兩年多。他說，住在華盛頓的居民已習慣四處看到警察，但警力佈防如此嚴密，實在「有點瘋狂」。為了個人安全，他明天不會外出溜狗，「想像到有可能會發生的事，真的有點怕。這些事我以為只會在第三世界發生，從沒有想過會在美國發生。」<br />\n<br />\n..........................................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GQaGlzYNyBrv_malLsfbOOhAEeU=/2736x1824/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MIMRBOKPBZB7LHKSXVOIFBJVEU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGQaGlzYNyBrv_malLsfbOOhAEeU%3D%2F2736x1824%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMIMRBOKPBZB7LHKSXVOIFBJVEU.JPG&h=1a82ff3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbb546ffbd58ec0015cf79bbc748f40c2fe3060a","tid":2373224,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bc0d64eb9af7a83bea2363fab30af28663f9f3","tid":2373224,"uid":256837,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mns7sKr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmns7sKr.jpg&h=67c5a573&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8366320e0e8147c8b8a23f836cb366dc67f62be7","tid":2373224,"uid":178317,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"岩喇,美國人熟習下啦<br />\n雜種出巡都係咁上下規模"},{"pid":"011f832f96549983abe8de22b748eba0887a6030","tid":2373224,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:46:56.000Z","msg":"好似香港有示威活動咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a45d8c1ce2f9ffb23e4753fac64441f2ee55ed2","tid":2373224,"uid":12463,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"又話美國好民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f280bd1f3060433e0639ebdb0446df554caed6","tid":2373224,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:47:47.000Z","msg":"美利堅特別行政區"},{"pid":"3d599b34819d64b64a40120c8da1e27c0032e313","tid":2373224,"uid":13504,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"非法總統係咁"},{"pid":"889f55e8d2c6feec9614b93e920a218009a91bb6","tid":2373224,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8366320e0e8147c8b8a23f836cb366dc67f62be7","tid":2373224,"uid":178317,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:46:42.000Z"